1 thou sand (100,000) persons according to the Federal Decennial Census
2 or most recent population estimate, that plan to:
3 1. Install new playground equipment and travel surfaces; or
4 2. Update existing playground equipment and travel surfaces,
5 shall ensure that all material and equipment are fully inclusive and
6 accessible for adults and children of all ages.
7 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
